description: Jacobi form of weight 12 and index 1 associated with a nonexistent Niemeier lattice of Coxeter number 1.
comments: a(3)<0 (apparently the only negative term) so the lattice cannot exist. a(4n)+2*sum_{1<=r<=sqrt(4n)} a(4n-r^2) = A056947(n)
references: Eichler and Zagier, The Theory of Jacobi Forms, Birkhauser 1985
author: Kok Seng Chua (chuaks(AT)ihpc.nus.edu.sg), Jul 17 2000
